  "description": "The Figure-Eight knot is amphichiral — its matrix is symmetric (M[i][j] = M[j][i]). This creates a mirror-image stereo field where the left side of the spectrum reflects the right. Combined with 0.9 spread, this preset has a distinctive centered-yet-wide quality unlike any other knot type. LFO2 sways the spread slowly.",
